title: Live the Lifestyle That YOU Deserve! 1 BR Available In 55+ Community!
posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', 'Amenities to help 55 and better live their best.', 'Legends at Silver Lake Village offer gorgeous interiors, fully appointed kitchens, in-home washers and dryers, nine foot ceilings and a patio for your comfort.', 'The guest suite is perfect for hosting the grand-kids and other visiting family and friends.', 'Located just steps from St Anthony’s Silver Lake Village Shops (Cub Foods, Chipotle, Stone Cold Creamery, Walgreens, Coffee Shops and more).', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Open & Spacious Floor Plans', '- Card & Crafts Room', '- Planned Resident Events!', '- 24-Hour Fitness Center', '- Private Patio or Balcony Space', '- Energy-Star Range, Dishwasher, Refrigerator/Freezer & Built-In Microwave', '- 9-Foot Ceilings Throughout', '- Close to Grocery Stores, Restaurants, Coffee & Ice Cream Shops', 'We are a pet-friendly community.', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'The Legends at Silver Lake Village is a 55 or better senior community and participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Legends at Silver Lake Village', '2500 38th Avenue Northeast', 'St. Anthony, MN, 55421', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.']
